      • buildBy

        public By buildBy()
        Defines how to transform given object (field, class, etc) into By class used by webdriver to locate elements. Looks for one of FindBy, FindBys or FindAll field annotations. In case no annotaions provided for field, uses field name as 'id' or 'name'.
        指定者:
        buildBy 在类中 AbstractAnnotations
        返回:
        By object
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - when more than one annotation on a field provided
